---
import LegalLayout from "@/layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "@/lib/site";
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Website Disclaimer"
  description="Disclaimer regarding content and information on the Expedition Reading website."
  updated="April 2026"
>
  <h2>Informational purposes only</h2>
  <p>
    The content on this website is for general informational purposes about Expedition Reading's mission,
    programs, partners, and work. It is not intended as medical, legal, financial, or professional advice.
  </p>

  <h2>Accuracy</h2>
  <p>
    We make a good-faith effort to keep information on this site current and accurate. Impact statistics,
    partner lists, and program details may shift between updates. If you are relying on a specific figure
    for a grant application, press piece, or funding decision, please contact us directly for the most current numbers.
  </p>

  <h2>External links</h2>
  <p>
    Links to external sites are provided for convenience. We do not endorse and are not responsible for
    the content or policies of linked sites, including third-party research cited in our materials.
  </p>

  <h2>Research citations</h2>
  <p>
    Where we cite statistics about early literacy and its lifetime impact, we rely on publicly available
    research from sources including the National Center for Education Statistics, the Harvard Center on
    the Developing Child, and published work by researchers including James Heckman. We encourage readers
    to review the primary sources directly.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this disclaimer or about information on the site can be sent to
    <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.contactEmail}</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
